Description: Offers basic high level access to the C 'wcslib' library for projecting and deprojecting [x,y] and [RA,Dec] image data using a target WCS. Comes bundled with 'wcslib' v7.1 downloaded from <https://www.atnf.csiro.au/people/mcalabre/WCS/>.
